        {
          "id": "msg_0aec61cb-5182-407d-98ab-d7926f23e025",
          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "That level of stress can feel like carrying everything at once. If you can, pause for a moment: unclench your jaw, drop your shoulders, and take three slow breaths. Then choose one priority for today and let “good enough” be enough for the rest.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-25T11:40:17.667Z"
        },
